  <h1>When do I <em>actually</em> need a Pap?</h1>
  <p class="dek">The cadence has changed. Here's how ACOG thinks about it now, and what we recommend for most patients.</p>
  <div class="meta">
    <span class="byline">By <em>Dr. Symone</em></span>
    <span class="rule"></span>
    <span>Dec 2025</span>
    <span class="rule"></span>
    <span>4 min read</span>
  </div>
</section>

