<div class="art-body">
  <aside class="side-left">
    <h5>In this piece</h5>
    <ul>
      <li class="active">The short answer</li>
      <li>Ages 21–29</li>
      <li>Ages 30–65</li>
      <li>After 65</li>
      <li>Why the change</li>
      <li>When to deviate</li>
    </ul>
    <h5>Share</h5>
    <div class="share">
      <a href="#">Email this →</a>
